## Maintenance

This bibliography is updated:
- When a new tag is introduced in a protocol (the author adds the entry
  immediately, not later)
- When a guideline issues a new version (the entry is updated; the tag
  may be retained or replaced depending on whether the protocol's
  recommendations changed)
- Annually as part of the library quality review (verify URLs, check for
  current versions of cited guidelines)

The "Last verified" date should be updated whenever the citation is
checked against the source. Citations with "Last verified: pending"
need source verification before any protocol using them reaches APPROVED.
